{"sections":[],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"There are no steps needed to migrate to 1.16 of the Composable Architecture, but there has been","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a change to the underlying behavior of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".appStorage"},{"type":"text","text":" that one should be aware of. When using"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":".appStorage","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" with ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@Shared"},{"type":"text","text":", if your key does not contain the characters “.” or “@”, then changes"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"to that key in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UserDefaults"},{"type":"text","text":" will be observed using key-value observing (KVO)."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Otherwise, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NotificationCenter"},{"type":"text","text":" will be used to observe changes."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"KVO is a far more efficient way of observing changes to ","type":"text"},{"code":"UserDefaults","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and it works cross-process,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as from widgets and app extensions. However, KVO does not work when the keys contain “.”"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"or “@”, and so in those cases we must use the cruder tool of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NotificationCenter"},{"type":"text","text":". That is not"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as efficient, and it forces us to perform a thread-hop when the notification is posted before","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"we can update the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@Shared"},{"type":"text","text":" value. For this reason it is not possible to animate changes that are"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"made directly to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UserDefaults"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["withAnimation {","  \/\/ ⚠️ This will not animate any SwiftUI views using '@Shared(.appStorage(\"co.pointfree.count\"))'","  UserDefaults.standard.set(0, forKey: \"co.pointfree.count\")","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In general, we recommend using other delimeters for your keys, such as “\/”, “:”, “-”, etc.:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["@Shared(.appStorage(\"co:pointfree:count\")) var count = 0"]}]}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17.1","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.15","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.14","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.13","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.12","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.11","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.10","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.9","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.8","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.7","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableA